title: Reflecting on The Most Searched Questions of the Year
description:
As 2021 comes to an end, Chelsea and Judah reflect on the year by discussing the top trending searches of the year. They answer the questions you Googled, from “How to be mindful” to “How to be happy alone.” All that and more on this week’s In Good Faith.
